            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿بِيَوۡمِ ٱلدِّينِ﴾: بُوقُوعِ يَومِ الجَزاءِ.</h2>"
        },
        "12": {
            "verses": {
                "83:12": {
                    "id": 12
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿مُعۡتَدٍ﴾: ظالِمٍ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿أَثِيمٍ﴾: كَثِيرِ الإِثْمِ.</h2>"
        },
        "13": {
            "verses": {
                "83:13": {
                    "id": 13
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿أَسَٰطِيرُ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ﴾: أباطِيلُ السَّابِقِينَ.</h2>"
        },
        "14": {
            "verses": {
                "83:14": {
                    "id": 14
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿رَانَ عَلَىٰ قُلُوبِهِم مَّا كَانُواْ يَكۡسِبُونَ﴾: غَطَّى عَلى قُلُوبِهِم كَثْرَةُ ما يَرْتَكِبُونَهُ مِنَ الذُّنُوبِ.</p>"
        },
        "15": {
            "verses": {
                "83:15": {
                    "id": 15
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿عَن رَّبِّهِمۡ﴾: عَن رُؤْيَةِ رَبِّهِم جَلَّ وَعَلَا.</h2>\n<h2>﴿لَمَحۡجُوبُونَ﴾: لَمَمْنُوعُونَ.</h2>"
        },
        "16": {
            "verses": {
                "83:16": {
                    "id": 16
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿لَصَالُواْ ٱلۡجَحِيمِ﴾: لَدَاخِلُو النَّارِ.</h2>"
        },
        "17": {
            "verses": {
