                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿كِتَٰبٞ مَّرۡقُومٞ﴾: مَكْتُوبٌ كِتابَةً بَيِّنةً.</h2>"
        },
        "21": {
            "verses": {
                "83:21": {
                    "id": 21
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿يَشۡهَدُهُ﴾: يَطَّلِعُ عَلَيهِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿ٱلۡمُقَرَّبُونَ﴾: الملائكةُ المُقرَّبُونَ مِنَ اللهِ.</h2>"
        },
        "22": {
            "verses": {
                "83:22": {
                    "id": 22
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿ٱلۡأَبۡرَارَ﴾: أَهْلَ الصِّدقِ والطَّاعَةِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿لَفِي نَعِيمٍ﴾: لَفِي الجنَّةِ يَتَنَعَّمُونَ.</h2>"
        },
        "23": {
            "verses": {
                "83:23": {
                    "id": 23
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿ٱلۡأَرَآئِكِ﴾: الأَسِرَّةِ.</h2>\n<p>﴿يَنظُرُونَ﴾: يَنْظُرُونَ إلى رَبِّهِم، وَإلى ما أَعَدَّ لَهُم مِنْ خَيراتٍ.</p>"
        },
        "24": {
            "verses": {
                "83:24": {
                    "id": 24
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿نَضۡرَةَ ٱلنَّعِيمِ﴾: بَهْجَةَ النَّعِيمِ وحُسْنَه.</h2>"
        },
        "25": {
            "verses": {
                "83:25": {
                    "id": 25
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿رَحِيقٖ﴾: خَمْرٍ صافِيةٍ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿مَخۡتُومٍ﴾: مُحْكَمٍ إِناؤُها.</h2>"
        },
        "26": {
            "verses": {
                "83:26": {
                    "id": 26
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿خِتَٰمُهُۥ﴾: آخِرُهُ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿مِسۡكٞ﴾: رائِحَةُ مِسْكٍ.</h2>\n<p>﴿فَلۡيَتَنَافَسِ ٱلۡمُتَنَٰفِسُونَ﴾: فَليَتَسابَقِ المُتَسابِقُونَ.</p>"
        },
        "27": {
            "verses": {
                "83:27": {
                    "id": 27
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَمِزَاجُهُۥ مِن تَسۡنِيمٍ﴾: وخَلْطُه مِنْ عَينٍ في الجنَّةِ تُعْرَفُ بـ «تَسْنِيمٍ».</p>"
        },
        "28": {
            "verses": {
                "83:28": {
                    "id": 28
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿يَشۡرَبُ بِهَا﴾: أَيْ: مِنْهاَ.</h2>\n<p>﴿ٱلۡمُقَرَّبُونَ﴾: الأَبْرارُ المقَرَّبون مِن اللهِ، المُكَرَّمون في الجَنَّةِ.</p>"
        },
        "29": {
            "verses": {
                "83:29": {
                    "id": 29
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿أَجۡرَمُواْ﴾: ارْتَكَبُوا الإثمَ العَظِيمَ، وهو الشِّرْكُ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿يَضۡحَكُونَ﴾: يَهْزَؤُونَ.</h2>"
        },
        "30": {
            "verses": {
                "83:30": {
                    "id": 30
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿يَتَغَامَزُونَ﴾: يُشِيرُونَ بأطْرافِ العُيُونِ سُخْرِيَةً بِهم.</p>"
        },
        "31": {
            "verses": {
                "83:31": {
                    "id": 31
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَإِذَا ٱنقَلَبُوٓاْ﴾: رَجَعُوا.</h2>\n<p>﴿فَكِهِينَ﴾: مُتَفَكِّهِينَ بالسُّخْرِيَةِ مِنَ المُؤْمِنِينَ.</p>"
        },
        "32": {
            "verses": {
                "83:32": {
                    "id": 32
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿رَأَوۡهُمۡ﴾: رَأَى هَؤُلاءِ الكُفَّارُ أَصْحابَ مُحَمَّدٍ ﷺ.</p>"
        },
        "33": {
            "verses": {
                "83:33": {
                    "id": 33
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
